# Udyam Registration Form (Steps 1 & 2 Clone)

A responsive web application that mimics the first two steps of the [Udyam Registration Portal](https://udyamregistration.gov.in/UdyamRegistration.aspx):  
1. Aadhaar + OTP Validation  
2. PAN Validation  

This is for demonstration purposes only â€” no real Aadhaar/PAN verification is performed.

## ğŸš€ Features
- Step 1: Aadhaar Number, Name as per Aadhaar, Mobile OTP simulation  
- Step 2: PAN Number, Name as per PAN  
- Real-time validation for Aadhaar (12 digits) and PAN (`[A-Za-z]{5}[0-9]{4}[A-Za-z]{1}`)  
- Mobile-first responsive design  
- PostgreSQL database for storing submissions  
- REST API for backend validation and storage  
- Unit tests for validation and API endpoints  
- Dummy OTP 123456

## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack
**Frontend:** React.js / Next.js, CSS3  
**Backend:** Node.js, Express.js, PostgreSQL (`pg` library)  
**Testing:** Jest  

